ActDepartment of Agriculture and Agri-Food Act
PrecisAuthority is requested for the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to be assigned the power to encourage and support development, innovation and growth in the co-operatives sector, and also to support co-operative projects that respond to public policy priorities by implementing the Co-operatives Development (Co-operative Development Initiative) and Business Development - Federal only initiatives components of Growing Forward.
